{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"2ce48f2114","title":"甘肃省通渭县城关人民公社党委会对右派分子的处理意见","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2798a45941","index":0,"year":1961,"month":12,"day":24,"articleId":"2ce48f2114"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"5b2eb5662f","type":"title","text":"甘肃省通渭县城关人民公社党委会对右派分子的处理意见","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"cc7d978624","type":"paragraph","text":"自1960年12月2日至1961年12月21日","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"87cb2f90f1","type":"paragraph","text":"卷内共5件20页\t\t\t\t\t\t保管期限   永久","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"572fb1e89f","type":"paragraph","text":"全宗号1\t\t\t\t\t\t\t归档时案卷号：4","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"3b1a73c92e","type":"subtitle","text":"关于右派份子处理的逐步意见","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"7d1c2c44ca","type":"paragraph","text":"我社共有返乡的右派份子7人，现在家劳动改造的只有4人，其余3人自回家后不仅没参加劳动，受广大群众的监督教育并且常不归家，此时不在，因此表现无处可报，现在家4人的处理意见列于后：","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"51f8882045","type":"paragraph","text":"孙效武，虽劳动不好，但没有其它事实，所以还是摘掉帽子继续加强教育进行思想改造。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"25af7787d6","type":"appellation","text":"王立轩，自回家后，一贯能遵守纪律，受群众的监督教育改造自己，据此经研究应摘掉帽子。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"8c84870b89","type":"paragraph","text":"孔令文，劳动一般，较能服从队上的领导，再没其它问题，因之这次还是摘掉继续加强思想教育。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"f453aed38a","type":"paragraph","text":"田庆荣，据说在外处某地已摘了帽子。","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"fdaa852657","type":"paragraph","text":"除此外其他3人（田成兰，景吉昌，米尚义）目前还是查清下落，发现所属单位作研究处理，若最近回来者劳动一个时期再视其改造情况：","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"173c14b9de","type":"paragraph","text":"是否有当请指正.","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"},{"id":"aa1fa1c3c0","type":"paragraph","text":" 中共城关公社委员会。61.12.24","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114"}],"page":{"id":"a191ba642a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"2ce48f2114","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}